<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="huge-adj">huge <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hjuːdʒ/    美 /hjuːdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-enormous-vast">1.★ <strong>巨大的；庞大的 (enormous / vast)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a huge amount / sum / quantity</strong> of money
一大笔钱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That's <strong>a huge success</strong>!
那是极大的成功！</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>hugely /'hjuːdʒli/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These traditional stories about Hawaii were hugely popular with tourists.
这些有关夏威夷的传统故事很受游客欢迎。</p><footer>2019全国改</footer></div></div>